:0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"做定帛金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttvLTbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttvLTbL.jpg&h=774d691a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"一定唔可以死!!"},{"pid":"02a5b205072a4132f8c9035d6b4a2271cc80a70d","tid":1967873,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"答左就會比軍政府炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9246b876b2272f3be1b9a275c5828f96a9bd7568","tid":1967873,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a878b9c0b0934dd4a7503989c6eff13afdc41285","tid":1967873,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"做定帛金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttvLTbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttvLTbL.jpg&h=774d691a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"比夠兩蚊，好事成雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0b7aae5f412c98ba2a725bf6b8ef0905d8e997","tid":1967873,"uid":269481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"我要開香檳慶祝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fe4cd9da25cafdb2a73e5027a3d17aeed102bc","tid":1967873,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T11:22:47.000Z","msg":"[CCTVB戰線] 美國網民玩死電視台嘅成功例子<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avicQKU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avicQKU</a>"}]}